{"name":"Process documents with Google Drive and Airtable and log the results","nodes":[{"parameters":{"rule":{"interval":[{"field":"hours","hoursInterval":6}]}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[-270,400],"id":"d14d2b52-a80a-4f3c-8b43-ab81ddd126f5","name":"Hourly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"operation":"download","fileId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"id","value":"={{ $json.id || $json.fileId }}"},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleDrive","typeVersion":3,"position":[54,400],"id":"60b56393-37e2-4add-af8d-b78bff7c3092","name":"Download from Google Drive","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"operation":"xlsx","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.extractFromFile","typeVersion":1,"position":[378,400],"id":"f1678771-3e43-48c7-a76d-2b7a3b648c4c","name":"Parse XLSX Contents"},{"parameters":{"mode":"runOnceForAllItems","jsCode":"// Normalize incoming document records to a stable schema\nconst out = [];\nfor (const item of $input.all()) {\n  const j = item.json;\n  out.push({ json: {\n    documentId: String(j.documentId ?? j.id ?? '').trim(),\n    fileName: typeof j.fileName === 'string' ? j.fileName.trim() : j.fileName ?? null,\n    source: j.source ?? 'api',\n    receivedAt: new Date().toISOString(),\n  } });\n}\nreturn out;"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[702,400],"id":"5038da1c-20f0-4fdd-930f-e291e27f1e3a","name":"Clean & Reshape Rows"},{"parameters":{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"5c0d1370-2c2c-46d4-bc60-cdcb41b992c8","leftValue":"={{ $json.documentId }}","rightValue":"","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"notEmpty"}}],"combinator":"and"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.if","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[1026,400],"id":"a30ee06e-cf1c-4245-9edb-3b4e8a0415e1","name":"Rows Pass Validation?"},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Document Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.airtable","typeVersion":2.1,"position":[1350,880],"id":"4b5a95b9-3766-41dc-858f-d6d0cd6b5091","name":"Quarantine Bad Rows","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"operation":"upsert","base":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Document Processing Base"},"table":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Documents"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":["documentId"],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.airtable","typeVersion":2.1,"position":[1674,400],"id":"588753d9-9387-4c47-a2f6-db200774362c","name":"Load Rows into Airtable","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"operation":"xlsx","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.convertToFile","typeVersion":1.1,"position":[1998,400],"id":"a522249f-5924-4e67-978f-28aabaf04a7d","name":"Repack as XLSX"},{"parameters":{"operation":"upload","name":"={{ 'processed-' + $now.toFormat('yyyyLLdd') + '.xlsx' }}","driveId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"My Drive"},"folderId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Processed"},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleDrive","typeVersion":3,"position":[2322,400],"id":"ab28877b-a92c-4e02-9b4e-cf058a7a0945","name":"Archive Processed File (Google Drive)","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"operation":"getCurrentDate","outputFieldName":"completedAt","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.dateTime","typeVersion":2,"position":[2646,400],"id":"1c5dcf9e-6ec7-40da-bf6b-977a748ba8f7","name":"Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"dataToSave":{"values":[{"key":"runId","value":"={{ $execution.id }}"},{"key":"itemCount","value":"={{ $items().length }}"}]}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.executionData","typeVersion":1,"position":[2970,400],"id":"e3d0082d-531a-40d5-a68e-107a37c9ada0","name":"Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"method":"GET","url":"https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup","sendQuery":true,"queryParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"query","value":"={{ $json.fileName }}"}]},"options":{"timeout":15000}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[3294,400],"id":"c1845bab-35c0-4c28-8940-7260064f6260","name":"Enrich with Reference Data","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"alwaysOutputData":true,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"305d3209-dff0-4bba-8388-cf378e1fb2be","name":"enrichedAt","value":"={{ $now.toISO() }}","type":"string"},{"id":"a7a4158c-cf22-4100-a0fc-b8c8b7931971","name":"enrichmentSource","value":"reference-api","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[3618,400],"id":"fe1d92ad-e345-496c-8810-b1019df1e56c","name":"Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"operation":"csv","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.convertToFile","typeVersion":1.1,"position":[3942,400],"id":"392f0274-b03e-45aa-983e-242be2d7c921","name":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"operation":"upload","name":"=run-{{ $now.toFormat('yyyyLLdd-HHmm') }}.csv","driveId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"My Drive"},"folderId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Archives"},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleDrive","typeVersion":3,"position":[4266,400],"id":"49855fb6-efad-41b3-b5bc-3b7778ae9944","name":"Archive Copy to Google Drive","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"operation":"read","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Document Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[4590,400],"id":"1408b741-8076-422b-9557-fa28a6da8444","name":"Load Previous Snapshot","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"alwaysOutputData":true,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"mode":"runOnceForAllItems","jsCode":"// Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\nconst current = $input.first().json;\nconst prev = $('Load Previous Snapshot').first().json || {};\nconst drift = {};\nfor (const k of Object.keys(current)) {\n  if (typeof current[k] === 'number' && typeof prev[k] === 'number' && prev[k] !== 0) {\n    drift[k] = Math.round(((current[k] - prev[k]) / prev[k]) * 1000) / 10;\n  }\n}\nreturn [{ json: { ...current, driftPct: drift, hasDrift: Object.values(drift).some(v => Math.abs(v) > 10) } }];"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[4914,400],"id":"8f9bbfbd-2352-4f5e-8a6e-e1a8b4445f3c","name":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"214c4e1c-6d58-48dd-8b0e-bd82c2fbcfe7","name":"runAt","value":"={{ $now.toISO() }}","type":"string"},{"id":"b4b20ce2-c096-484b-ad82-46c132a4345d","name":"itemCount","value":"={{ $input.all().length }}","type":"number"},{"id":"575ceb0a-97b1-4fef-9fe5-0f02e40b4944","name":"status","value":"completed","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[5238,400],"id":"9a1a2fd5-f9cc-49b2-a3ee-99379e41b18f","name":"Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"operation":"create","base":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Document Processing Base"},"table":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Documents"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.airtable","typeVersion":2.1,"position":[5562,400],"id":"e6a04556-8077-484d-a6ce-e7023396afbe","name":"Append Audit Row (Airtable)","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#docs","cachedResultName":"#docs"},"text":"=✅ Process documents with Google Drive and Airtable and log the results — run completed at {{ $now.toFormat('HH:mm') }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[5886,400],"id":"66f52938-8782-4f37-b8c9-df113c916af6","name":"Send Summary to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"5f72ea96-99a9-4692-8df9-d98c234f2728","name":"failedNode","value":"={{ $json.error?.node?.name || 'unknown' }}","type":"string"},{"id":"79ae5802-90a5-4786-83e2-96d0a467eb62","name":"errorMessage","value":"={{ $json.error?.message || JSON.stringify($json).slice(0,200) }}","type":"string"},{"id":"d3ec9726-ebef-4786-96f6-5d6e57d01a49","name":"workflow","value":"={{ $workflow.name }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[5238,1420],"id":"7f137e26-f1d8-443c-89d2-b3fc4121f777","name":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#docs","cachedResultName":"#docs"},"text":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[5562,1420],"id":"9a16d256-df18-40eb-a628-ee0cfdbc59ad","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Document Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[5886,1420],"id":"5da5a55b-9bec-4d30-8ef1-30f4dbbf4b80","name":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hourly Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — every 6 h. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Download from Google Drive","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"f7fd6b38-0d6c-f1c8-266e-efca9c3041d2","name":"Note: Hourly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Download from Google Drive\n\ngoogleDrive — `download` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Parse XLSX Contents · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"02fe1f17-d783-0ff1-b0e8-a2a1e4110d7b","name":"Note: Download from Google Drive"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Parse XLSX Contents\n\nParses the incoming XLSX binary into JSON items.\n\nNext: Clean & Reshape Rows","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"db759920-fb70-b149-b383-cb9d8c5f4dba","name":"Note: Parse XLSX Contents"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Clean & Reshape Rows\n\nCustom JavaScript: Normalize incoming document records to a stable schema\n\nNext: Rows Pass Validation?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"d1f2233b-8268-06af-f91e-4b2aadb4297d","name":"Note: Clean & Reshape Rows"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Rows Pass Validation?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.documentId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Load Rows into Airtable · ②→ Quarantine Bad Rows","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"1f866039-c62e-353f-e168-73939cd715b7","name":"Note: Rows Pass Validation?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Quarantine Bad Rows\n\nairtable — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,1000],"id":"defa6733-4606-b3d6-4c1f-20e9368513b6","name":"Note: Quarantine Bad Rows"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Rows into Airtable\n\nairtable — `upsert` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Repack as XLSX · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"e978b221-9b44-66d5-b845-210ed8cfb4e3","name":"Note: Load Rows into Airtable"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Repack as XLSX\n\nSerializes items to a XLSX binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Processed File (Google Drive)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,520],"id":"1e98437c-72f0-bbae-3863-565e33cc03b3","name":"Note: Repack as XLSX"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Processed File (Google Drive)\n\ngoogleDrive — `upload` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Stamp Completion Time · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"03ffcfa9-1cbf-6e9d-4d82-b1581231f519","name":"Note: Archive Processed File (Google Drive)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"17c9c1f2-087c-acca-016e-b39e81c574eb","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Enrich with Reference Data","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"79c8cba4-e3e0-8a4b-786f-93630fede9d9","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"8e7218e4-d73f-1f33-9259-65a8cb8abc1b","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"c8a35a5e-6a18-6ab9-1c07-9fdbcb056b67","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Copy to Google Drive","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"a984f83a-d9bc-0dc7-4416-f09b1b146c11","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Copy to Google Drive\n\ngoogleDrive — `upload` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Load Previous Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"c8f8fac9-0963-d2c3-49ba-cef59ed87ea1","name":"Note: Archive Copy to Google Drive"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"2326de08-ee17-84c6-220e-5e98522cc4db","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"1a362dd8-d1b0-db48-60d8-b4a571617871","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Airtable)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"47119cfa-1601-e9c0-851d-647aa46231e2","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Airtable)\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"112bc3ee-5951-dbce-4914-7526b4300ff7","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Airtable)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"4243d586-98a3-f07e-e22d-26c14d776020","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,1540],"id":"8cd9da30-7bbe-516c-9cbf-5eca70ce9c8a","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,1540],"id":"0bde64c3-2fcf-0dfe-d78f-b2d29dfab5a5","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,1540],"id":"b771bc27-8893-a08c-af76-092334635161","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Process documents with Google Drive and Airtable and log the results\n\n**Pattern:** File Processing · **Level:** Production · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nProcess documents with Google Drive and Airtable and log the results. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual contracts is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nHourly Schedule → Download from Google Drive → Parse XLSX Contents → Clean & Reshape Rows → Rows Pass Validation? → Load Rows into Airtable → Repack as XLSX → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to file processing without manual effort\n- Anyone automating contracts in legal\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Standardizes the process every time\n- Responds in seconds\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Airtable PAT; Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"1f2261c5-d9ee-ad5c-4072-d0cba1f1fc20","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"8e7f6b47-de03-fffd-bd4c-14a5bc8019c5","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your contracts process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"7db89c7b-cdd0-24b9-9ae3-33694ac04d02","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Hourly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Download from Google Drive","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Download from Google Drive":{"main":[[{"node":"Parse XLSX Contents","type":"main","i